Description: root directory for a DID's resources containing links to subdirectories
subdirectory containing links to a DID's profiles
subdirectory containing links to a DID's keychains
subdirectory containing links to a DID's accounts (i.e. crypto or Oauth)
subdirectory containing links to a DID's social connections (i.e. follows)
subdirectory containing links to a DID's data collections (i.e. app data)
subdirectory containing links to a DID's services (i.e. notifications or backup)
subdirectory containing links to a DID's settings documents (i.e. internationalization
